snippet.title: Flying Feathers (Commodore 64) Playthrough (Beating Default Highscore, Game Then Crashes)
snippet.description:
Around 3 minutes to beat the in-game highscore of 10,000 points. Win condition based on TMR video. The game seems endless otherwise. The game crashed at around 18,000 points. Better off anyway.

Stay tuned !!
